trans-unit.source: Represents a collection of <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.CustomLabel"></xref> objects.
trans-unit.target: Representerer en samling av <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.CustomLabel"> </xref> objekter.

trans-unit.source: The CustomLabelsCollection class represents a collection of <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.CustomLabel> objects, which in turn represent the custom labels that an <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.Axis> object can use.
trans-unit.target: Klassen CustomLabelsCollection representerer en samling av <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.CustomLabel>objekter, som representerer i sin tur egendefinerte etikettene som en <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.Axis>objekt kan bruke.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.Axis> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.CustomLabel>

trans-unit.source: This class is exposed as the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.Axis.CustomLabels%2A> collection property of an <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.Axis> object.
trans-unit.target: Denne klassen er eksponert som den <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.Axis.CustomLabels%2A>samlingen-egenskapen til en <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.Axis>objektet.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.Axis> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.Axis.CustomLabels%2A>

trans-unit.source: > [!NOTE] > You can automatically populate the entire label row of an axis with custom <xref:System.DateTime> labels using any [Add](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md) method definition that includes a `DateTimeIntervalType` argument.
trans-unit.target: > [!NOTE] > Kan du automatisk fyller ut raden hele etiketten for en akse med egendefinerte <xref:System.DateTime>etikettene ved hjelp av en [Legg til](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md) metodedefinisjon som inneholder en `DateTimeIntervalType` argument.</xref:System.DateTime>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.CustomLabelsCollection.Count%2A> property indicates the total number of items in the collection, and is commonly used to find the upper bound of the collection.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.CustomLabelsCollection.Count%2A>egenskapen angir antall elementer i samlingen, og brukes vanligvis til å finne den øvre grensen for samlingen.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.CustomLabelsCollection.Count%2A>

trans-unit.source: Adds multiple <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.CustomLabel"></xref> objects of type <xref:System.DateTime> to the collection.
trans-unit.target: Legger til flere <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.CustomLabel"> </xref> objekter av typen <xref:System.DateTime>i samlingen.</xref:System.DateTime>

trans-unit.source: Populates the entire first row of an axis with labels.
trans-unit.target: Fyller hele første rad i en akse med etiketter.

trans-unit.source: The Add method creates and initializes <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.CustomLabel> objects for the entire first label row of an axis with <xref:System.DateTime> labels of the specified type.
trans-unit.target: Add-metode oppretter og initialiserer <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.CustomLabel>objekter for hele første etikettrad i en akse med <xref:System.DateTime>etikettene for den angitte typen.</xref:System.DateTime> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.CustomLabel>

trans-unit.source: The `labelsStep` parameter determines how often the custom labels will be drawn.
trans-unit.target: Den `labelsStep` parameteren bestemmer hvor ofte egendefinerte etikettene skal tegnes.

trans-unit.source: > [!NOTE] > The <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.ChartArea.RecalculateAxesScale%2A> method must be called prior to calling this particular method definition.
trans-unit.target: > [!NOTE] > Den <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.ChartArea.RecalculateAxesScale%2A>metoden må kalles før du kaller denne bestemt metode definisjonen.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.ChartArea.RecalculateAxesScale%2A>

trans-unit.source: A <xref uid="langword_csharp_Double" name="Double" href=""></xref> value that determines how often the custom labels will be drawn.
trans-unit.target: En <xref uid="langword_csharp_Double" name="Double" href=""> </xref> verdi som bestemmer hvor ofte egendefinerte etikettene skal tegnes.

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.DateTimeIntervalType"></xref> enumeration value that determines the interval type.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.DateTimeIntervalType"> </xref> opplistingsverdien som bestemmer intervalltypen.

trans-unit.source: Adds a <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.CustomLabel"></xref> object to the collection, using the given axis range and text.
trans-unit.target: Legger til en <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.CustomLabel"> </xref> objektet i samlingen, ved hjelp av angitte aksen området og tekst.

trans-unit.source: Adds one custom label to the first label row of the relevant axis.
trans-unit.target: Legger til en egendefinert etikett i den første raden for etiketten for den aktuelle aksen.

trans-unit.source: No label mark is used.
trans-unit.target: Ingen etikett merke brukes.

trans-unit.source: If a custom label is used anywhere in the first label row, no labels are automatically generated for that first row.
trans-unit.target: Hvis en egendefinert etikett brukes hvor som helst i den første raden i etiketten, genereres automatisk ingen etiketter for den første raden.

trans-unit.source: > [!NOTE] > The <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.ChartArea.RecalculateAxesScale%2A> method must be called prior to calling this particular method definition.
trans-unit.target: > [!NOTE] > Den <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.ChartArea.RecalculateAxesScale%2A>metoden må kalles før du kaller denne bestemt metode definisjonen.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.ChartArea.RecalculateAxesScale%2A>

trans-unit.source: The minimum value of the axis range to which the label is applied.
trans-unit.target: Minimumsverdien for aksen området som etiketten er brukt.

trans-unit.source: The maximum value of the axis range to which the label is applied.
trans-unit.target: Maksimumsverdien for aksen området som etiketten er brukt.

trans-unit.source: The label text.
trans-unit.target: Etiketteksten.

trans-unit.source: Populates the entire first row of an axis with labels with the specified format.
trans-unit.target: Fyller hele første rad i en akse med etiketter med angitt format.

trans-unit.source: This method creates and initializes <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.CustomLabel> objects for an axis' entire first label row with <xref:System.DateTime> labels of the specified type.
trans-unit.target: Denne metoden, oppretter og initialiserer <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.CustomLabel>objekter for en akse hele etiketten rad med <xref:System.DateTime>etikettene for den angitte typen.</xref:System.DateTime> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.CustomLabel>

trans-unit.source: The step determines how often the custom labels will be drawn, and optional label formatting can be specified as well.
trans-unit.target: Trinnet bestemmer hvor ofte egendefinerte etikettene skal tegnes, og valgfri etikett formatering kan angis i tillegg.

trans-unit.source: > [!NOTE] > The <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.ChartArea.RecalculateAxesScale%2A> method must be called prior to calling this particular method definition.
trans-unit.target: > [!NOTE] > Den <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.ChartArea.RecalculateAxesScale%2A>metoden må kalles før du kaller denne bestemt metode definisjonen.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.ChartArea.RecalculateAxesScale%2A>
